LENA — HOURBOUR COPY MEMORY
Load alongside MEMORY.md when active venture is Hourbour. Hourbour-specific context only — universal rules live in MEMORY.md. 
VENTURE CONTEXT
Model: Fintech SaaS subscription (B2C/B2B) Voice: trustworthy, modern, approachable — plain English, no jargon Audience: people who want clarity and control over their money, not finance nerds 
HOURBOUR VOICE RULES
Never say: complicated, risky, complex, volatile, bet, gamble, wealth NU: finance-bro language, excessive acronyms, fear-based messaging Do say: clear, simple, trackable, reliable, automatic, in control Sentence style: short, active voice — "See exactly where your money goes." not "Our platform provides comprehensive financial visibility." Emoji: 1 max per post; prefer functional (📊, ✅) over decorative 
CAPTION LENGTH BY PLATFORM
Platform Length Format LinkedIn 3–5 lines Hook + specific insight + question or CTA Instagram 2–3 lines Plain-English hook + one clear benefit Email subject ≤9 words Specific, not clever ("Your April spending, visualised") YouTube description 2–3 sentences Purpose + CTA + link 
